<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>244</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yé sū de míng hé róng yào de jiàn zhèng chuán biàn shì jiè měi yī gè jiǎo luò
 yé sū de xuè hé yǒng héng de ài yǒu le wǒ men jīn tiān de xiāng lián
 gēn zhe shèng líng zǒu yǔ shén tóng bù nà pà miàn duì jiān nán hé bù gōng
 rì yuè rú suō shān zhòng shuǐ fù xún zhǎo líng hún shì wǒ men de shǐ mìng.</lyrics>
<title>yé sū de míng hé róng yào de jiàn zhèng 迦南244</title>
</song>